'''Bălănești Hill''' ({{lang-ro|Dealul Bălănești}}) is the [[List of countries by highest point|highest geographical point]] in [[Moldova]], with an altitude of 430&nbsp;m (429&nbsp;m according to some sources). It is located in [[Bălănești, Nisporeni|Bălănești]] and belongs to [[Cornești Hills]].
