{{Infobox protected area | name = Ferlo Sud Wildlife Reserve | alt_name = Réserve de Faune du Ferlo-Sud | iucn_category = IV | photo = | photo_alt = | photo_caption = | photo_width = | map = Senegal | map_alt = Map of Senegal showing the location of the Ferlo-Sud Wildlife Reserve protected area | map_caption = Location in Senegal | map_width = | mark = Location dot green.svg | marker_size = 16 | location = [[Senegal]] | nearest_city = Loungue Tekodie | coordinates = {{coord|14.833335|N|13.999994|W|type:landmark_region:SN_scale:50000|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | area = {{Convert|6337|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}} | established = 1972<!--{{start date|1972|MM|dd}}--> | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | governing_body = | world_heritage_site = | url = }}
The '''Ferlo Sud Wildlife Reserve''' ({{lang-fr|Réserve de Faune du Ferlo-Sud}}), established in 1972, is a {{Convert|6337|km2|sqmi}} [[IUCN Protected Area Management Categories|IUCN habitat and species protected]] [[nature reserve]] located in [[Senegal]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://protectedplanet.net/sites/Ferlo_Sud_Wildlife_Reserve |title=Ferlo Sud Wildlife Reserve |publisher=World Database on Protected Areas: Protected Planet |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606162502/http://protectedplanet.net/sites/Ferlo_Sud_Wildlife_Reserve |archivedate=2012-06-06 |df= }}</ref> The nature reserve is bordered by the [[Ferlo Nord Wildlife Reserve]] to the north.
