'''Nabi Yunis''' is the highest point of the [[Palestinian territories]], with an altitude of 1,030&nbsp;metres (3,350&nbsp;ft).<ref>[http://poica.org/2007/03/a-house-demolished-three-others-threatened-in-the-town-of-halhul/ A house demolished, three others threatened in the town of Halhul - 24 March,2007], POICA, retrieved 2017-01-21.</ref><ref>[http://www.peakbagger.com/peak.aspx?pid=10457 West Bank High Point, Palestinian Authority], Peakbagger, retrieved 2012-10-14.</ref> It is located in the town of [[Halhul]], [[Hebron Governorate]].
