'''Protected areas of Norway''' include:
* [[National parks of Norway]]
* [[:Category:Nature_reserves_in_Norway]]

About 17 percent of the mainland of Norway is protected. Of this, ca. 8.3 percent is national parks, 1.3 percent is nature reserves and 4.7 percent otherwise protected.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.miljostatus.no/templates/themepage____2258.aspx |author=Unknown |title=Vernet natur. Miljøstatus Norge. |date=2007 |language=Norwegian |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527223630/http://www.miljostatus.no/templates/themepage____2258.aspx |archivedate=2008-05-27 |df= }}
</ref>

[[IUCN]] aims to protect at least 15 percent of all types of nature.
