mani people|Roma]] [[2011 Bulgaria antiziganist protests|demonstration]].<ref name=bbc-timeline /> ** [[Armeets Arena]] and Sofia Arsenal Museum of Contemporary Art opens. ** Sopharma Business Center towers built. * 2012 ** [[Knyaginya Maria Luiza Metro Station]] opens. ** Population: 1,241,396. * 2013 ** February: [[Protests against the Borisov cabinet|Protest against the Borisov cabinet]]. ** June: [[Protests against the Oresharski cabinet|Protest against the Oresharski cabinet]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://noresharski.com/category/the-protest/?lang=en |title=The Protest |location=Sofia |publisher=Noresharski.com |editor=Nikolay Staykov |accessdate=28 December 2013 |quote=Antigovernment Press Centre }}</ref>
